Cell["Continue the conversation with \"yoda1\":", "Text",
 TaggingRules->{},
 CellChangeTimes->{3.98733085841466*^9},
 CellID->1941798359,ExpressionUUID->"471b3b7f-476c-4dba-8ef7-9b024e277819"],

Cell["\<\
LLMChat 'since when do you use a green light saber?' --chat-id=yoda1

# Green, my lightsaber is, yes. Symbol of a Jedi Consular, it is. Wisdom and \
harmony, it represents. Since my training as a Jedi, I have wielded it. A \
sign of my connection with the Force, green blades are. Hmm. Use it wisely, I \
do.\
\>", "ExternalLanguage",
 TaggingRules->{
